com.rscja.deviceapi

Class RFIDWithISO14443A4CPU

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rscja.deviceapi.RFIDBase
      • com.rscja.deviceapi.RFIDWithISO14443A4CPU
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRFIDBase, IRFIDWithISO14443A4CPU

    public class RFIDWithISO14443A4CPU
extends RFIDBase
implements IRFIDWithISO14443A4CPU
    RFID模块ISO14443A CPU卡协议操作类
    RFID module ISO14443A CPU card protocol operation type

    注意：
    Attention:
    1、使用前请确认您的机器已安装此模块。
    1. Make sure this module is installed before you use your device.
    2、要正常使用模块需要在\libs\armeabi\目录放置libDeviceAPI.so文件
    2. Put libDeviceAPI.so file in directory \libs\armeabi\ then module can be used normally.
    3、在操作设备前需要调用 RFIDBase.init() 打开设备，使用完后调用 RFIDBase.free() 关闭设备
    3. Call RFIDBase.init() to switch on the device before operating the device, call RFIDBase.free() to switch off device after using.

    Author:
    liuruifeng
